item.title: CVE-2023-40309|2024-09-28T22:10:46.845Z -- sap_se -- sap%20commoncryptolib
item.description: SAP CommonCryptoLib does not perform necessary authentication checks, which may result in missing or wrong authorization checks for an authenticated user, resulting in escalation of privileges. Depending on the application and the level of privileges acquired,Â an attacker could abuse functionality restricted to a particular user group as well as read, modify or delete restricted data.
